- Reads AuditIR via load_audit_ir + raw manifest.json for fields the loader
  doesn't expose (scope.decision_id, retrieval.{started_at,finished_at,
  latency_ms,queries_executed,pool_id}, models.{generator,evaluator})
- Sovereignty cascade: non-cleared sources excluded from pool.sources;
  sentences citing excluded sources rebuilt via constructor (validators
  enforced, NOT model_copy) with verifier_pass=False + drop_reason="invalid_token"
  + evaluator_agrees=False
- section_status="dropped" when all sentences fail post-cascade
- SovereigntyFilterEmptiedReportError when all sections drop -> 422
- SourceTier normalization: T4+/UNKNOWN -> T3 with raw_tier in provenance
