- Provenance token regex (canonical fallback) extracts evidence_id from
  [#ev:<id>:<start>-<end>] strings
- AuditIR EvidenceSpanToken -> string token serialization

bundle.py:
- NEW GET /runs/{run_id}/bundle.tar.gz endpoint
- Resolves run_id -> artifact_dir via run_store
- Status codes: 200 (signed tar.gz), 404 (not found/incomplete/missing dir),
  422 (aborted/sovereignty-emptied), 503 (signer unavailable)
- Explicit Depends(get_sign_fn) injection (lazy import keeps top-of-file clean)

