- Happy path: synthetic AuditIR fixture -> 3 valid Pydantic models
- Sovereignty cascade: T2-cited sentences redacted, T1-cited kept
- Sovereignty-emptied: SovereigntyFilterEmptiedReportError raised
- Section drops when no passing sentences remain

