Addresses Codex diff iter-1 findings:

P1-001 — Depends() callable identity:
- Move get_sign_fn import to module top (NOT lazy inside lambda)
- Depends(get_sign_fn) now matches the callable that create_app() registers
  in app.dependency_overrides — production signer override now fires
- Removed lambda + _resolve_sign_fn() helper; FastAPI's dependency injection
  is keyed by callable identity, lambdas break that

P2-001 — partial_* PipelineVerdict mapping:
- Pipeline-A partial_* runs HAVE kept sections; they're "success-with-
  degradation" not "abort_no_verified_sections"
- Collapse partial_* into PipelineVerdict="success" so the slice-chain
  validator accepts them (degradation recorded on manifest, not verdict)
- Previously: partial_* → abort_no_verified_sections → pydantic
  ValidationError → 500. Now: 200 signed bundle.

P2-002 — endpoint test coverage:
- NEW tests/polaris_v6/api/test_bundle_endpoint_targz.py (5 tests)
- 404 when run missing / lifecycle != completed
- 422 when aborted
- 503 when signer unconfigured (proves bridge ran + Depends wired)
- 200 (or non-503) when signer override fires (P1-001 regression catch)

Smoke: 49/49 pass in tests/polaris_v6/api/ (bridge + endpoint + pre-existing).

